## Forensic Log (Click-to-Data + AI + Aesthetic)

### 1) Subscription & Modular Isolation

- **[FILE PATH]** `app/tech-ops/page.jsx`  
  **[ELEMENT]** Entire Tech-Ops route surface  
  **[TRACE RESULT]** Route renders directly from shell + mode data; no subscription guard in page-level logic.  
  **[DISCREPANCY]** A miidle-only user is not explicitly blocked by entitlement checks.  
  **[CORRECTION]**
  ```ts
